<NPR>NOTE:  This guide specification covers the requirements for <SCP>safety procedures 
and requirements for the demolition, removal, encapsulation, and disposal of 
asbestos containing materials (ACM)</SCP>.  This specification is used in conjunction 
with Section <SRF>01 35 26</SRF> GOVERNMENT SAFETY REQUIREMENTS.<BRK/>
<BRK/>
Adhere to <URL HREF="http://www.wbdg.org/ffc/dod/unified-facilities-criteria-ufc/ufc-1-300-02">UFC 1-300-02</URL> Unified Facilities Guide Specifications (UFGS) Format 
