<BRK/>
<NPR>The use of this section in the contract specification means that known asbestos 
material is involved.  Estimate the quantity and specify as unit price items 
in Section 00 21 13, INSTRUCTIONS TO BIDDERS or Section <SRF>01 20 00.00 20</SRF> Price 
and Payment Procedures per standard practice of the activity preparing the contract.</NPR><BRK/>
<AST/><BRK/></NTE>
<NTE><BRK/>
<AST/><BRK/>
