of requirements in the contract.  The plan must include but not be limited to the precise personal protective 
equipment to be used including, but not limited to, respiratory protection, type of whole-body protection[ and 
if reusable coveralls are to be employed decontamination methods (operations and quality control plan)], the 
location of asbestos control areas including clean and dirty areas, buffer zones, showers, storage areas, change 
