 0.15 mm</MET><ENG> 6-mil</ENG> plastic sheet sealed with tape to prevent water or other damage.  Provide two layers of<MET> 0.15 mm</MET><ENG>
 6-mil</ENG> plastic sheet over floors and extend a minimum of<MET> 300 mm</MET><ENG> 12 inches</ENG> up walls.  Seal all joints with tape.  
