<BRK/>
<LST INDENT="-0.33">a.  Local exhaust ventilation equipped with HEPA filter;</LST><BRK/>
<BRK/>
<LST INDENT="-0.33">b.  Enclosure or isolation of processes producing asbestos dust;</LST><BRK/>
<BRK/>
<LST INDENT="-0.33">c.  Where the feasible engineering and work practice controls are not sufficient to reduce employee exposure 
