<BRK/></SPT>
<SPT><TTL>Unacceptable Practices</TTL><BRK/>
<BRK/>
<TXT>The following work practices must not be used:</TXT><BRK/>
<BRK/>
<LST INDENT="-0.33">a.  High-speed abrasive disc saws that are not equipped with point of cut ventilator or enclosures with 
